LEO PRIME&#39;s optics were the one&#39;s of a soldier&#39;s as he looked at
STRAIGHT SHOT as he watched her leave. &quot;Such faith she has in her
brother.&quot; he said quietly to LORD ELDER.

ELDER nodded, &quot;She has a point. It may be that soome of the Predacons
may learn to change, Blackarachnia did for a while.&quot;

There was a grim smile, &quot;Yes, but where is she now? We haven&#39;t seen
her in years.&quot; He looked at ELDER, &quot;Go look after them, i am sure
there is some grumbling.&quot;

There was a nod from ELDER as he turned and began walking towards the
docking bay, his optics dim in thought.

